flowchart TB
    JOB[Classification Job]
    PROCESS[Process Job]
    ACK[Acknowledge]
    RETRY{Retry Count < 3?}
    DLQ[Dead Letter Queue]
    BACKOFF[Exponential Backoff]
    ALERT[Alert Team]
    LOG[Log Error Details]

    JOB --> PROCESS
    PROCESS -->|Success| ACK
    PROCESS -->|Transient Error| RETRY
    PROCESS -->|Permanent Error| DLQ
    RETRY -->|Yes| BACKOFF
    RETRY -->|No| DLQ
    BACKOFF --> PROCESS
    DLQ --> ALERT
    DLQ --> LOG
